description: The spike in cases comes as Dmitry Peskov, President Putin's spokesman, confirms he tested positive.
title: Coronavirus: Russia now has second highest virus case total
title_page: Coronavirus: Russia now has second highest virus case total - BBC News
maintext: The outbreak is far from over, the president warned, saying that "danger remains". But all sectors of the economy should begin to restart, he said - though local authorities could bring in tougher restrictions if needed to contain the spread of the virus.
